ZH: 在这个重要的时刻，作为领导者，我认为义不容辞。
EN: At this crucial moment, as a leader, I believe it is my duty to step up.

ZH: 作为公民，我们有义不容辞的责任为社会做出贡献。
EN: As citizens, we have an undeniable responsibility to contribute to society.

ZH: 作为家长，我们有义不容辞地教育我们的孩子。
EN: As parents, it is our duty to educate our children without fail.

ZH: 作为团队成员，每个人都有义不容辞地完成自己的工作。
EN: As team members, everyone has a duty to fulfill their responsibilities without hesitation.

ZH: 在面对重大决策时，我们要有义不容辞地承担风险。
EN: When facing important decisions, we must take on risks without hesitation.

ZH: 我们必须义不容辞地保护我们的自然环境。
EN: We must protect our natural environment without fail.

ZH: 在社会发展的过程中，我们有义不容辞地遵守法律。
EN: In the process of social development, we must adhere to the law without question.

ZH: 义不容辞地帮助有需要的人是我们每个人的责任。
EN: It is our responsibility to help those in need without hesitation.

ZH: 在困难时期，我们有义不容辞地相互支持。
EN: In times of difficulty, we must support each other without question.

ZH: 在冲突时，我们有义不容辞地寻求和解。
EN: In times of conflict, we must seek reconciliation without hesitation.

ZH: 义不容辞地反对任何形式的歧视和不公平对待。
EN: We must stand against all forms of discrimination and unfair treatment without hesitation.

ZH: 作为学生，我们有义不容辞地努力学习。
EN: As students, it is our duty to study diligently without fail.

ZH: 在工作中，我们有义不容辞地完成我们的任务。
EN: In our work, we must fulfill our tasks without question.

ZH: 作为领导者，我们有义不容辞地引领团队走向成功。
EN: As leaders, we must lead our team to success without hesitation.

ZH: 在做任何决定之前，我们都有义不容辞地考虑影响。
EN: Before making any decisions, we should consider the consequences without fail.

ZH: 在保护动物方面，我们有义不容辞地提倡尊重生命。
EN: When it comes to protecting animals, we must advocate for respecting all life without question.

ZH: 义不容辞地维护我们的尊严和价值观是至关重要的。
EN: Upholding our dignity and values without fail is crucial.

ZH: 在任何情况下，我们有义不容辞地捍卫我们的权利。
EN: In any situation, we must defend our rights without hesitation.

ZH: 作为社会一员，我们有义不容辞地参与社会进步。
EN: As members of society, we must participate in social progress without question.

ZH: 在支持公平竞争方面，我们有义不容辞地遵守规则。
EN: When it comes to supporting fair competition, we must adhere to the rules without hesitation.
